# `kustomize build --enable-helm` materialises Helm charts under
# `charts/` next to each kustomization that references them. The
# charts are pinned by `version:` in the kustomization and re-fetched
# on each render, so the cache directories are not tracked. Slice 17
# (add-local-k3s-obs-cluster) adds a second tree at `infra/k8s-obs/`
# with the same pattern.
infra/k8s/**/charts/
infra/k8s-obs/**/charts/

# Slice 19 (add-cross-cluster-mtls). Private key material for the
# cross-cluster self-signed CA and the per-cluster leaf certs stays
# out of git. Per-directory `.gitignore`s in each `certs/` dir cover
# this too — this repo-root entry is defence-in-depth so a future
# certs/ directory cannot accidentally leak a key.
infra/**/certs/*.key
